pageContext.claim: “And they won't be coming through anymore. It's been almost 100 percent effective in the areas that it's been built. … And in all of those areas where the wall has been put up, it's virtually 100 percent effective.”
pageContext.analysis: It's hard to take this Trump claim seriously since he will often segue into saying that the wall is being built in batches and people can get in wherever there are unfinished areas.
